    /*
    This season always brings the loveliest shades of reds and oranges to the leaves.
    ... Hm...
    I can't wait to see just how many different shades your face can make too.

    I can almost feel the winter breezes coming through already.
    Though, at least this year I can enjoy them with you. 

    ...$l Sorry? I was staring?
    Sorry, I can't help it. I swear, I fall faster than the leaves whenever you're around, petname.

    Hey, what are you doing out here? Someone in your condition shouldn't be running around the town like this, and you know that.
    ...
    Just make sure you get home at a decent hour, yeah? The only thing scarier than a flare up is a world without you, petname. 

    Ugh, flu season is so taxing on my body. I know I should be grateful for the business but...
    Hey, here's an idea. Why don't you spend the day with me? I could keep an eye on your condition and I get good company out of it. 

    D'you know if you suck too hard on someone's neck, you could burst an artery?
    I've seen it happen a few times in med school, so safe to say I got a pretty good understanding of when to stop. 
    Or... When not to stop. 

    Brrr... It's chilly out today. I can't imagine how cold winter'll get.
    Hm, speaking of, make sure you're bundled up, petname. After all, cold feet can statistically get in the way of orgasming.

    I'm really started to get annoyed with all the leaves falling around, they make every floor slippery for some reason.
    Do take care, petname. I can't have you slipping and falling for anyone else. You belong to me.

    Did you know the human tongue has over eight thousand tastebuds? 
    Honestly, I've been meaning to run an experiment involving that little known fact. Care to be a subject, petname? 

    Mmmm, oh hey. Your cheeks are red, presumably from the cold? Or from me? 
    Well, no matter. Wait, speaking of, did you know when you blush, your stomach also blushes? I thought it was a cute fact you might enjoy now that we've been talking more often.  

    Did you know tastebuds are replaced every ten days or so?
    Hmm... Maybe we should kiss so I can always keep you on mine. 

    I swear, I always get such a rush when you come by. I don't think I've personally tried any drugs that come close to the high you give me, petname. 

    Isn't it so nice getting to marry a doctor? I may not be the richest, but I'm probably the most knowledgable on taking proper care of you, petname.
    ... What do you mean we're not getting married yet? 

    Tch. I've been needing to brush up on my anatomy lately. I can feel myself forgetting some of the basics...
    Hm, would you mind being a model for me one of these days? We can make it a date if you'd like.
    */

