    /*
    Hmm... I guess now that it's winter you finally have enough time for me--
    Err... your treatments. You'll be coming by a lot more frequently, right?

    Make sure you're washing your hands frequently, yeah? You're immunocompromised due to your disease and I'd hate how bad the flu would feel to someone in your condition. 

    Please, petname, be sure you're drinking and eating something that's nice and warm during this cold season.
    I'd offer a suggestion, but I don't want to be too forward just yet. 

    You look a bit flush, are you feeling alright?
    I don't have my thermometer on me, but using my lips against your forehead would quickly test if you're running a fever.
    Could I try?

    ...
    Ugh, sorry, I just can't put my name on-Oh, Crocus! That's what it's called...
    Anyways, did you know that the spice harvested from the flower has several terribly interesting medicinal properties, @? 
    It has anti-depressant, anti-inflammatory, and… sedative properties.

    Oh, you're shivering! 
    Here, come with me, I'll get you something warm to drink and a blanket, yeah?_I'd rather you warm me up yourself._Oh... @... I love where you're thinking but you're still getting the blanket. Doctor's orders._Thank you..._Anything for my favorite patient. 

    Jeez, I can't believe the year's already coming to an end.
    Am I crazy or do I feel like I barely know you? I know I have all your medical records but...
    I want to know everything about you, petname. 

    Oh, your lips look dry.
    I mean, if you're interested, I have a salve or two which might be able to help. 

    If you're ever needing a change of scenery, feel free to rest in my apartment above the clinic.
    Knowing where you are means I worry less anyway. 

    I swear, I knew from the moment we met that you'd be someone special to me.
    Do you think we could professional relationship aside and get to know each other better?

    ...$a
    Hm? Oh, sorry, I got into a tussle with another patient this morning. 
    I guess they can't all be as {{LDescript}} as you.

    %Harvey seems distracted, listing a few conditions and their known symptoms, almost like he's quizzing himself so he won't forget.
    ...
    Oh, @! Sorry, didn't see you there.
    Yoba, with the way you keep sneaking up on me, it can't be good for my heart. 

    Oh, you look stressed today. Is it the disease flaring up? 
    Do you need to come to the back and rest for a bit? You worry me, petname.

    I've been reading the most fascinating journal lately. It's been giving me some wonderful ideas for new treatments on your condition. 
    I hope this doesn't make you feel like too much of a guinea pig, but I can't help it.

    Hey, I know it's a little early but, I was hoping you'd wear this.
    I found it outside the mines and the light reminded me so much of your eyes. [888] //glowstone ring
    */

