    /*
    Oh, you're shivering... Here, let me help.
    %Harvey takes your hands, bringing them to his lips, seemingly to ghost his lips over them.
    Sorry, I needed to be selfish. My lips were blue from the cold as well. 

    Do you have enough blankets and firewood? I know that house must be cold without me in it. 

    Mmmm... Days like this always make me want to cuddle up next to a fireplace with my favorite person...
    Maybe partake in some more 'warming' activities as well...

    Have you ever made snow angels before?
    Well, I'm sure with how angelic you are, petname, they'd be perfect every time. 

    Oh, I hate to sound needy but could you spend the night?
    My heater ran out and it's too cold to sleep without someone else... 

    Has anyone ever told you just how warming your smile is? 
    I swear, it always feels like a few degrees rise when we're in the same room. 

    Y'know, the best way for me to monitor your health is for you to come by more often. 
    Or, I could move in finally. I know that little farmhouse of yours is cold without me. 

    You know a kiss could increase a person's pulse rate to 100 beats per minute or more.
    I mean, I've got a stethoscope at the ready if you'd like to try.

    ...$l#$b#Sorry, sometimes I like to imagine what it'd be like if our roles were reversed. It'd be cute to see you taking care of me, but I think it'd be best if we kept the medicine to me, yeah, petname?

    I had the strangest dream about you last night...
    Say, do you think it'd be hard to tie you down? Maybe rope would do the trick or... No, you'd need something more medicinal...

    Until we can observe local traditions, I was hoping you could...
    Err... I was hoping you could wear this. I wanted you to have something that'd symbolize my ever growing love and want for you, petname... [527] // iridium band
    I hope it'll guide you back to me if you ever get lost. 

    Hey, I got you something that I thought you'd like. [74] //prismatic shard
    Hm? Where'd I get a prismatic shard? Oh... Er... Marlon gave it to me last time I went up near the mines to...
    Sorry, do the details really matter? 

    Here, this is for you. [72] //diamond
    Did you know that diamonds are actually made after being subjected to intense heat and pressure? 
    I'd love to see how you'd turn out under similar conditions...

    ...$l
    Sorry, your cheeks have such a lovely pink glow to them in this weather. 
    I swear, I wish you'd hide away in my apartment so only I could be the one to see you like this.
    */

