    "AfterDark.Strings.Harvey.HarveyRoom.1": "A comparison between fighter planes of the Ferngill Republic and the Gotoro Empire.",
    "AfterDark.Strings.Harvey.HarveyRoom.2": "There's a beautiful view of the sky above Stardew Valley.",
    "AfterDark.Strings.Harvey.HarveyRoom.3": "It's Harvey's model airplane collection.",
    "AfterDark.Strings.Harvey.HarveyRoom.4": "It's Harvey's model airplane collection.",
    "AfterDark.Strings.Harvey.HarveyRoom.5": "It's a complicated radio broadcasting set.",
